<include src="tutorial.xml"/>
<tutorial>
<stage title="Capture the Wool">
<message>
<line>
`rThis map is a four team Capture the Wool (CTW) map
</line>
<line>
The objective is to grab one wool from each of the opposing
</line>
<line>teams sides, and return it to your base.</line>
</message>
<teleport>
<point yaw="0" pitch="50">99,63,-180</point>
</teleport>
</stage>
<stage title="Purple Team Base">
<message>
<line>
`rThis is the `5Purple Team's `rbase. You spawn with gear ready to go into battle!
</line>
<line>
You can find Iron Blocks inside your base, and use them to craft armor
</line>
</message>
<teleport>
<point yaw="0">99,7,-5</point>
</teleport>
</stage>
<stage title="Red Wool Rooms">
<message>
<line>These are `4Red `4team's `rwool rooms.</line>
<line>
The `4Red Team `rshould defend these rooms against all attackers from the three other teams who will be trying to steal the wool and make it back alive.
</line>
<line>
In order for players from the opposing teams to capture the red wool, they must run into the wool room with their teams corresponding color.
</line>
<line>
For example, players from the `5Purple Team`r, will be running into the room with purple clay around it. They cannot go into the wool rooms for the `6Orange`r, or `2Green`r teams.
</line>
<line>
There are special goodies inside that will help you fight your way out.
</line>
</message>
<teleport>
<point yaw="90" pitch="50">-73,37,-180</point>
</teleport>
</stage>
<stage title="Victory Monument">
<message>
<line>This the `5Purple Teams`r Victory Monument.</line>
<line>
The `5Purple Team`r must return one each of the opposing teams wools, to win the match!
</line>
</message>
<teleport>
<point yaw="0">99,7,22</point>
</teleport>
</stage>
<stage title="Center Island">
<message>
<line>
This is the center island! There is a spawner that spawns different types of gear, which may be very useful to gain an advantage over your opponents.
</line>
</message>
<teleport>
<point yaw="180" pitch="30">99,25,-158</point>
</teleport>
</stage>
</tutorial>
